title: TV | Keith Lemon's Back T'future Tribute
text: As you must have heard at this stage, today marks the actual date that Marty McFly travelled to in the 1989 movie Back to the Future 2, so it's very much a highly anticipated day for fans of the franchise and members of the human race in general. To mark it, comedian and Celebrity Juice presenter Keith Lemon will host this very special tribute show where he will recreate famous scenes from the iconic movie with the help of some celebrity guests, including Gino D'Acampo, Tom Davis, McBusted, Paddy McGuinness, Hank Osasuna and Ashley Roberts.
